Female genitalia (
Fig. 21
). Ovipositor narrow, elongated, apophyses anteriores and posteriores thin, almost equal in length; antrum funnel-like, slightly sclerotised; ductus bursae moderate in length, flattened, sclerotised; corpus bursae long, narrow in caudal part, sack-like extended in proximal part.
